  "strategy": [
    "Alternate between short forward moves and scanning rotations to maximize marker detection.",
    "Commit to a single rotation direction or forward move to avoid oscillations.",
    "Prioritize moving toward the marker as soon as it is seen, using a dedicated pursuit commit state.",
    "After encountering obstacles, perform recovery (backward or rotate) followed by a scan before resuming forward movement.",
    "Enforce stop only when close to the marker to ensure safe task completion.",
    "Never allow move_forward in response to obstacle_front; always pass through a recovery state.",
    "Use commit states to enforce consistent action execution until a safe or goal state is reached.",
    "After losing the marker, immediately return to scanning rather than exploration.",
    "Maintain explicit transitions for all uncontrollable events in every state."
  ]
